    {
      "id": "18c4750c-f3ba-817c-ae93-c589800332ff",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Work uses multiple data mining techniques on data from 98 undergraduate students. Authors distinguish between active and passive learners and then extract features for predictive modeling.",
