    {
      "id": "18c4750c-f3ba-8173-8166-d35a41474b80",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Instructors rely on LMS to provide basic data in the interactions between student and the contents. This makes this sort of data especially appealing. However, at the time of the paper, there is limited research going into the data generated by LMS. However, the potential of the statistical analysis of these logs is recognized.",
